This is one of my favorite meals. I've made it many times and always vary the ingredients based on what I have on hand. It's always wonderful. It gets raves from my family and guests. Even my daughter who shys away from chicken will eat it. I'd recommend that you always used the herb crust, as it seems to make the meal. I never use leek or turnips; instead I use spinach, potato and mushrooms. This is the best pot pie I've ever had.

